{"tid":1497903,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人幾時先肯徹底咁羞辱黑警","createTime":"2019-08-23T07:33:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T09:33:03.000Z","uid":200606,"like":53,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d7bf23e82d2ff61507683842c8d3318e3b535bc1","tid":1497903,"uid":200606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:33:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\">黑警暴行罄竹難書</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑 警 死 全 家</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n入返正題，雖然個個都憎到黑警入骨<br />\n但係平時行街見到有狗車經過竟然可以相安無事，完全冇人屌......有啲失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我要佢地去到邊都抬唔起頭做人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去撚到天涯海角都比人精神虐待 生不如死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">應有此報</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n好期待有黑警俾市民鬧到精神失常，崩潰，最後發癲吞槍自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家由今日開始，見一隻屌一隻，有幾毒就鬧幾毒，將佢地推落懸崖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e012e18dfbe27d825db3a14e2dd864a91322abb","tid":1497903,"uid":25108,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:34:29.000Z","msg":"對家無限權力大<br />\n你一叫就拉你<br />\n點鬥"},{"pid":"3e55dcae650f8157238e6acc3c24087f5696cd25","tid":1497903,"uid":11281,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:35:17.000Z","msg":"有冇人會list 哂出嚟 貼街招 ， 特別係女警 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係要俾全香港睇下 不停airdrop出去"},{"pid":"627a3566e1eaa6feaad4c6b26ef72f348aebf2f8","tid":1497903,"uid":200606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"自推十次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警不得好死<br />\n到時咪撚出嚟扮慘話大家都係香港人<br />\n我屌你老母臭閪全家上下死清光<br />\n出撚得嚟行就預撚咗要還<br />\n你估做咁多仆街嘢可以安安樂樂過下半世？</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"b6d61aec25eaed4336991fc0c517ed1a960b0dbd","tid":1497903,"uid":200606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c88db040ec29dfd714fd3028c55eba1728da982c","tid":1497903,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:36:56.000Z","msg":"大佬，罵完入差狗屋畀人打死<br />\n<br />\n家陣誰大誰惡誰正確"},{"pid":"b35bf0a3d93aa9f3a9002d5b2ba5c696aa7234c5","tid":1497903,"uid":101498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:37:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">是日（823星期五）活動<br />\n銀髮族罷買<br />\n會計界遊行<br />